	<string>Camera access is required to add camera sources to the compositor.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Microphone access is required to add audio sources to the compositor.</string>
	<key>NSHomeDirectoryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Home directory access is required to read media files.</string>
	<key>NSVideoUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Videos folder access is required to save recordings.</string>
	<key>NSScreenCaptureUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Screen capture access is required to add the screen as a source in the compositor.</string>
